		<item>
		<title>How to send a broadcast message to Viber contacts</title>
		<link>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/how-to-send-a-broadcast-message-to-viber-contacts/</link>
					<comments>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/how-to-send-a-broadcast-message-to-viber-contacts/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Oluwafemi Lawrence]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 08 Jun 2023 17:25:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">https://docs.chatrace.com/?post_type=kb&#038;p=2974</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[The broadcast tool allows you to send messages to multiple contacts simultaneously in an automated manner. It helps businesses to send announcements, discounts, updates, and]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>The broadcast tool allows you to send messages to multiple contacts simultaneously in an automated manner. It helps businesses to send announcements, discounts, updates, and other notifications to their contacts.</p>



<p>Follow the steps below to send a broadcast message to your Viber contacts.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="How to send broadcast message on Viber" width="780" height="439" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/V5D-LJzrOPk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">1 &#8211; Create your flow</h4>



<p>Go to Menu &gt; Flows and click the <strong>Add</strong> button. You can watch this <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IkU6_JnHabE" target="_blank">video</a> to learn how to create a flow.</p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="495" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_132959517-1024x495.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2935" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_132959517-1024x495.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_132959517-300x145.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_132959517-768x371.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_132959517-1536x743.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_132959517.png 1870w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>


<h4 class="wp-block-heading">2 &#8211; Send your flow to your contact list</h4>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="495" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_130122349-1024x495.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2924" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_130122349-1024x495.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_130122349-300x145.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_130122349-768x371.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_130122349-1536x743.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-02_130122349.png 1870w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>Select the <strong>Viber</strong> channel to proceed.&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="488" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180648577-1024x488.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2976" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180648577-1024x488.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180648577-300x143.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180648577-768x366.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180648577-1536x732.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180648577.png 1868w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p></p>



<p>Select your broadcast flow and click send</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="488" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180834304-1024x488.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2979" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180834304-1024x488.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180834304-300x143.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180834304-768x366.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180834304-1536x732.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-08_180834304.png 1868w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>
]]></content:encoded>
					
